OL,3,CBill on assisted dying faces key vote
OL,4,Cat Scottish Parliament
OL,6,FHolyrood will vote this evening on the
OL,7,Fgeneral principles of the Assisted
OL,8,FDying for Terminally Ill Adults
OL,9,F(Scotland) Bill ` with a majority of
OL,10,FMSPs needing to back the legislation
OL,11,Fif it is to continue its progress
OL,12,Fthrough the Scottish Parliament.
OL,14,FBoth opponents and supporters of
OL,15,Fassisted dying will stage
OL,16,Fdemonstrations outside Holyrood on
OL,17,FTuesday as MSPs prepare to cast their
OL,18,Fvotes.
