OL,6,FIf his bill passes on Tuesday evening,
OL,7,Fthe proposals will return to Holyrood
OL,8,Ffor further scrutiny and amendment
OL,9,Fbefore MSPs have a final vote on
OL,10,Fwhether it should become law.
OL,12,FMr McArthur, however, insisted that
OL,13,FScotland "cannot put off" debating
OL,14,Fassisted dying, and the Parliament
OL,15,F"cannot continue to leave this issue
OL,16,Fin the too difficult box".
